{
  "stem": "15174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How she managed to do all this, to go through all of this without my father, with me sick, going to all these offices, I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess-- I guess when you have to do something, you just do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it-- it amazes me that- that she was able to do all of this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In any case, in I guess it must have been March or April of 1939, we got word that we had a visa to Cuba.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my mother had to arrange for passage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she arranged that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She got passage for the three of us on the ship called the And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to pay for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I have no idea how she did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe we had some savings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I really don't know, but she did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then the problem was that my father was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were-- the ship was leaving from Hamburg, so he needed to come to Germany in order for us to leave together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what he needed was a transit visa, in other words, a visa saying that he could come in to Germany for three days or two days or whatever so that he could leave from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother, again she had to go to the offices and try to get this and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father, I guess he had to go to the German embassy or legation in Krakow to-- to get these papers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, we-- we had passage on the ship for May 14th, 1939.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we-- my mother had sold what she could.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
